      "span_text": "More recently, the area under the dose curve (AUC) measurement attempts to combine reactivity and sensitivity into one (Fig. 2c); it is similar to a coordinate system of sensitivity and reactivity, but also incorporates partial anergy induced at high allergen concentrations and can be calculated even in cases where responses do not t well to a typical dose-response curve"
